    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演一名夜班厨师，在一座快餐小食亭中努力工作吧。前一任厨师离奇失踪，只留下了你来破解悬案。在你忙于处理深夜订单的同时，怪异事件接二连三地发生。你能将零碎的线索拼凑起来，发掘消失案背后的真相吗？ <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126330/extras/2f37a0d37ec9670f07775b78b2014fc4.poster.avif?t=1762538146\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126330/extras/2f37a0d37ec9670f07775b78b2014fc4.webm?t=1762538146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>本作有三种模式：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>故事模式</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无尽模式（带有全球玩家排行榜）</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>休闲模式</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的职责是准备菜品，并通过亭子的窗户为顾客提供服务。用菜刀准备好食材，或是在亭中的烧烤台上烤肉。顾客们有时也会想要喝点东西，所以你得为他们准备好汽水与啤酒。你偶尔还需要在咖啡机上为他们煮上一杯热腾腾的咖啡。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126330/extras/0c15c92ccaeb317c239fd181b1270c48.poster.avif?t=1762538146\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126330/extras/0c15c92ccaeb317c239fd181b1270c48.webm?t=1762538146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细听取顾客们给出的线索，查明之前在这里工作的那个人身上发生了什么吧。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126330/extras/ecca5e8cb0ca6b10a711cf6158233951.poster.avif?t=1762538146\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3126330/extras/ecca5e8cb0ca6b10a711cf6158233951.webm?t=1762538146\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
